Well, here we are all sitting and waiting for the release of Vanguard. To help pass the time, I posted above my BIRTH OF A UNICORN story. Hope you liked it. If you did and are tired of checking your email box 20 times a day, I have a couple more stories based in the same world of Athero to distract you. Pop on over to my place (and yes, the stories are free <img src="images/smilies/emote_blink.gif" border="0" alt="" title="Suprised" class="inlineimg" />). At the same time, you can also get a peek at my long-awaited (well, by me, anyhow) novel, WITCHCANERY.  (By the way, before I posted this, I asked Fricka if it was okay.  She graciously said yes. <img src="images/smilies/emote_thumb.gif" border="0" alt="" title="Thumbs Up" class="inlineimg" /> )</div>
