    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_308987">I just wanted to let people know about the site where the other short stories are.  They are for free but I recently discovered that the default for ZenCart (the shopping cart used as <a href="http://www.fantasyfic.com" target="_blank">FantasyFic</a>) was to require people registering at the shop to give their street address and their telephone number.  Even *I* wouldn't register if I was required to do that.  Anyhow, it has been changed now to just asking for your name and email address.<br />
<br />
If anyone has already registered at FantasyFic Library (that's the name of it), please go into your registration and edit it.  If you put &quot;none&quot; in every spot, it will show none in the final result.  Sorry about that.</div>
